<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span> ضعيف ـ <span class="c2">((تخريج فقه السيرة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٤٠٨)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
